Wallpaper is a decorative wall covering used to enhance the beauty of interior walls. It is applied to walls to give rooms a stylish, modern, and attractive look. Wallpapers come in many designs such as floral patterns, geometric shapes, textures, abstract prints, nature themes, and 3D styles. They are also useful for covering minor wall imperfections and adding color or texture beyond what paint offers.

Common Prices of Wallpaper (Pakistan)

Prices depend on quality, material, and design:

Basic wallpaper: PKR 2,000 – 5,000 per roll
Premium wallpaper: PKR 5,000 – 12,000 per roll
Luxury / custom wallpaper: PKR 12,000+
Where It Is Used
Living room wall
Bedroom wall
TV lounge background
Office reception
Hallway / entrance
Feature walls